# 7. High-Level Architecture

```text
Application Repository
        │
        │ calls reusable workflow
        ▼
security-workflows
        │
        ├── checkout caller repository
        ├── prepare GitHub authentication
        ├── run pinned remediation-core
        ├── read result.json
        ├── create branch and commit
        └── create or update Pull Request
                    │
                    ▼
            remediation-core
                    │
          ┌─────────┴─────────┐
          ▼                   ▼
        Syft                 Grype
          │                   │
          └─────────┬─────────┘
                    ▼
           Normalized Findings
                    │
                    ▼
             Version Resolver
                    │
                    ▼
           Ecosystem Adapter
                    │
                    ▼
          Updated Dependency Files
                    │
                    ▼
               Verification
                    │
                    ▼
          Structured JSON Result
```

