# 8. Separation of Responsibilities

## Remediation Core

Input:

```json
{
  "directory": ".",
  "ecosystem": "auto",
  "minimum_severity": "high",
  "strategy": "minimum-safe",
  "allow_major": false,
  "maximum_updates": 1
}
```

Output:

```json
{
  "status": "VERIFIED_UPDATE",
  "ecosystem": "npm",
  "directory": ".",
  "dependency": {
    "name": "lodash",
    "from": "4.17.19",
    "to": "4.17.21",
    "relationship": "direct"
  },
  "vulnerabilities": [
    {
      "id": "CVE-2021-23337",
      "severity": "High"
    }
  ],
  "changed_files": [
    "package.json",
    "package-lock.json"
  ],
  "verification": {
    "target_findings_removed": true,
    "new_critical_findings": 0,
    "dependency_files_valid": true
  }
}
```

## Security Workflows

Input:

```text
Caller repository workspace
GitHub token
Reusable workflow inputs
remediation-core result.json
```

Output:

```text
Git branch
Git commit
Pull Request
GitHub job summary
SBOM artifacts
Scan artifacts
```

