# 27. Recommended Technical Decisions

```text
Core language             Go
Core delivery             GitHub Release CLI binary first, container later
Inventory                 Syft
Scanner                   Grype
Internal SBOM             Syft JSON
Evidence SBOM             CycloneDX JSON
First ecosystem           npm
First CI provider         GitHub Actions
First Git provider        GitHub
Workflow model            Reusable workflow
Configuration             .remediation.yml
Update strategy           minimum-safe
Allowed updates           patch and minor
PR granularity            one package per PR
Database                  none
Queue                     none
Auto-merge                disabled
Install scripts           disabled
```

